  * Addresses two cross site scripting issues:
    PMASA-2007-5, PMASA-2007-6
    (CVE-2007-5386, CVE-2007-5589, closes: #446451)

 -- Thijs Kinkhorst <thijs@debian.org>  Wed, 17 Oct 2007 22:54:41 +0200

